'''''Samson Against the Sheik''''' ({{lang-it|'''Maciste contro lo sceicco'''}}, also known as ''Maciste Against the Sheik'') is a [[List of Italian films of 1962|1962]] [[Cinema of Italy|Italian]] [[peplum film]] directed by [[Domenico Paolella]].<ref name="60z">{{cite book|last=Roberto Poppi, Mario Pecorari|title=Dizionario del cinema italiano. I film|publisher=Gremese Editore, 2007|isbn=8884405033}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Michele Giordano|title=Giganti buoni|publisher=Gremese Editore, 1998|isbn=8877421835}}</ref>

